
You will learn skills in this game by attempting to use them. For
instance the first time you go into a fight you will probably try
to dodge an attack, and then you also will gain a dodge skill. 

Type "skills" to list the skills you currently know.
Type "spells" to list the spells you currently know.
Type "prac" to list all skills and spells you currently know. 

See also: "help spell list", "help skill list","help status",
          "help casting",

